{"tid":882672,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近同樓上個印印。。。","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T02:59:44.000Z","uid":59290,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3fa07a2de64f2db96323753dcc534385fd6bb8","tid":882672,"uid":59290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:48:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最近岩岩grad，因為未諗到做咩就日日遊手好閒尻fing fing <br />\n<br />\n問題就黎，小弟每日都會4點落樓下食個tea散個步。咁都會撞到樓上個印印。講吓個印印先，大約2尾3頭有啲陳凱琳feel，肉地有波，大約160高。<br />\n<br />\n最初大家都會問侯吓，tea? 咁樣。慢慢熟就多野傾。大家會傾吓日常生活拍拖咁，亦知道佢係印尼有個老公。<br />\n<br />\n有次佢趁屋企冇人仲叫我上去一齊玩煮飯仔，對肉地係咁系埋黎真係扯扯地。<br />\n<br />\n前日我又上去佢度，食完野小個便點知佢突然入左黎鎖埋門。。。"},{"pid":"c45f0102ce2f23818e2e7681635f03f6a7491180","tid":882672,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"樓主等比人落降飲埋經血"},{"pid":"36eda75f09242ec9db578de838f568eece70ee23","tid":882672,"uid":118648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"純文字討論？"},{"pid":"e908d0f241270a4db88d8e9019ff4499d5b7ef87","tid":882672,"uid":41205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:51:37.000Z","msg":"巴打識食，香港班賓印個個都如狼似虎人間性器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64933e834902915ad93c4d335e79961fee7e7107","tid":882672,"uid":200247,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"無人想知，依家興食屎都周街講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6044302abad694ba43ff6fe226aa50fc6d2f0d20","tid":882672,"uid":59290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c45f0102ce2f23818e2e7681635f03f6a7491180","tid":882672,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"樓主等比人落降飲埋經血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"印尼有降頭咩<img src=\